    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要了解游戏最新资讯吗？欢迎大家加入QQ官方讨论组（978103657）!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今天，我们发布了游戏的最新试玩版，欢迎大家试玩体验呀！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《突破重围 Demo》是一款以火车为主题的卡牌构筑类肉鸽游戏，游戏中不断构筑属于自己的卡组，在紧张刺激的即时战斗中突破帝国军的重重阻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/b0aff8590c3693e055251d9b87372cc7.poster.avif?t=1768056698\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/b0aff8590c3693e055251d9b87372cc7.webm?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/b0aff8590c3693e055251d9b87372cc7.mp4?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・为了完成抵抗军给予你的重要任务，你必须驾驶能穿梭于不同星球的星际列车，突破帝国军的重重阻击，并最终完成你的使命。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿梭不同星球，开启一次次冒险任务</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・每一次游玩都是程序生成的全新冒险，在风格各异的星球间不停穿梭，遭遇各种各样的突发事件，以此获得各种装备强化列车，并招募各类佣兵加入你的队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・每一次的路线选择都充满了无限可能，是保守前进？还是刀尖跳舞？就在一念之间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/561ddd1edbf5510241b9e44d0aebe852.poster.avif?t=1768056698\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/561ddd1edbf5510241b9e44d0aebe852.webm?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/561ddd1edbf5510241b9e44d0aebe852.mp4?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>进入非常规战斗模式，体验即时卡牌的紧张刺激</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・与回合制的战斗不一样，即时战斗的过程更加紧张刺激与流畅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・结合卡牌构筑，给你带来完全不一样的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/0bdd525b29c1830d500bb4a79f0fec15.poster.avif?t=1768056698\" width=598 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/0bdd525b29c1830d500bb4a79f0fec15.webm?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/0bdd525b29c1830d500bb4a79f0fec15.mp4?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>烧脑组合策略，感受充满特色的卡组构筑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・每列火车都有丰富与独特的卡牌提供你选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・熟悉每一张卡牌的特效与机制，让你的战斗游刃有余。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/d40b2a726147c742cff10bcbf9b092e9.poster.avif?t=1768056698\" width=598 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/d40b2a726147c742cff10bcbf9b092e9.webm?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/d40b2a726147c742cff10bcbf9b092e9.mp4?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>坚持不懈突破重围，终将到达胜利的彼岸</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・失败不是结束，每一次的冒险都是通往传奇的过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・随着一次一次的冒险，解锁不同的卡牌，佣兵，能力，都将成为你突破重围的助力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/7553e8eda98f02064480a2a1c3cf5527.poster.avif?t=1768056698\" width=598 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/7553e8eda98f02064480a2a1c3cf5527.webm?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249780/extras/7553e8eda98f02064480a2a1c3cf5527.mp4?t=1768056698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
